# Changelog

All notable changes to the Agang SA website project will be documented in this file.

## Project Overview
**Project:** Agang SA Website  
**Purpose:** Digital platform for social, political, and community engagement in South Africa  
**Development Context:** Portfolio of Evidence (POE) for Web Development  
**Technologies:** HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JavaScript


### Part 1 - Initial Development
- **Basic website structure** with 10+ pages
- **CSS styling** with variables and consistent design
- **SEO optimization** with meta tags and descriptions

### Part 2 - Responsive Implementation  
- **Mobile navigation** with hamburger menu
- **Responsive grid layouts** for all pages
- **Typography scaling** for mobile devices
- **Image optimization** for different screen sizes


### Part 3 - Final Submission
- **Implemented form validation** with real-time error messages
- **Added interactive Google Maps** integration
- **Enhanced gallery lightbox** with keyboard navigation
- **Improved responsive design** across all devices
- **Added news search functionality** with dynamic filtering
---

