## [Unreleased]

### Added
- **Responsive Navigation:** Hamburger menu implementation for mobile devices
- **Mobile-First CSS:** Responsive design using media queries with mobile-first approach
- **Accessibility Improvements:** Semantic HTML structure, alt text for all images, ARIA roles implementation
- **SEO Optimization:** Meta tags (`description`, `keywords`, `author`) added to `<head>` section
- **Social Media Integration:** Social media links added to website footer
- **Multimedia Content:** Video thumbnail section with play button overlay feature

### Changed
- **Navigation Structure:** Updated for better usability across all devices
- **Layout Optimization:** Improved spacing and layout for mobile and tablet screens
- **Interactive Elements:** Enhanced button styles for better touch interaction
- **Accessibility Compliance:** Improved color contrast ratios for better readability
- **Hero Section:** Updated for optimal readability on small screens

### Fixed
- **CSS Path Correction:** Fixed `<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">` path issues
- **Content Accuracy:** Corrected typos in news section:
  - "Sucess" â†’ "Success"
  - "libarated" â†’ "liberated" 
