## [Version 1.0 - Part 1 Final] - 2025-01-25
### Added
- **Complete website deployment** with all 7 main pages
- **Homepage** (`index.html`) with hero section and featured content
- **About page** (`about.html`) with mission, vision, and values
- **News & Blog page** (`news.html`) for updates and articles
- **Campaigns page** (`campaign.html`) showcasing ongoing initiatives
- **Get Involved page** (`getinvolved.html`) for volunteer opportunities
- **Donation page** (`donate.html`) with contribution functionality
- **Contact page** (`contact.html`) with contact form and information

### Technical Implementation
- **HTML5 Semantic Structure:** Used `<header>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<article>`, `<footer>`
- **Basic CSS Styling:** Initial styling without full responsiveness
- **Navigation System:** Basic menu linking all pages
- **Content Hierarchy:** Proper heading structure (h1-h6) throughout all pages

### File Structure Finalized


