## [Unreleased]

### Planned JavaScript Enhancements
- **Form Validation System:** Advanced client-side validation for all forms
- **Interactive Maps:** Enhanced map functionality with custom markers
- **News Filtering:** Category-based filtering for news and blog sections
- **Performance Monitoring:** Analytics integration for user behavior tracking

