- **CSS Variables System:** Expanding `:root` variables for comprehensive theme management
- **Advanced Animations:** Implementing CSS keyframes for micro-interactions
- **Print Stylesheets:** Adding print media queries for better document printing

---

## [Version 2.3 - JavaScript Functionality] - 2025-11-01

### JavaScript Implementation

#### Added
- **Mobile Navigation System:**
  - Hamburger menu toggle functionality for mobile devices
  - Automatic menu closure when navigation links are clicked
  - Click-outside detection to close menu when clicking elsewhere
  - Robust error handling for pages without navigation elements

- **Payment Integration:**
  - Stripe donation form integration with secure payment processing
  - Client-side form validation and submission handling
  - Redirect functionality to Stripe Checkout sessions
  - Comprehensive error handling for payment failures

- **Event Management:**
  - DOMContentLoaded wrapper for proper script execution timing
  - Conditional element existence checking to prevent runtime errors
  - Modular code structure for maintainability

#### Changed
- **Code Architecture:**
  - Improved event listener organization and management
  - Enhanced error prevention through element validation
  - Streamlined form submission workflows

#### Fixed
- **Cross-Page Compatibility:**
  - Prevented JavaScript errors on pages without specific elements
  - Ensured consistent behavior across all website pages
  - Resolved mobile navigation reliability issues

### Technical Implementation Details

